com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.util

Class Filter.FilterBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.util.Filter.FilterBuilder
  • Enclosing class:
    Filter

    public static class Filter.FilterBuilder
extends Object
    Filter Builder for build collection queries.

    Usage:

     
 measurementApi.getMeasurements(
     Filter.build()
         .byFragmentType("com_telekom_example_SampleTemperatureSensor")
         .bySource("1122334455")
     );
